snippet.title: Nickelodeon All-Star Brawl: SpongeBob vs. Leonardo vs. April vs. Patrick Gameplay
snippet.description:
Check out gameplay of the four-player brawl featuring SpongeBob Squarepants and Patrick plus TMNT's Leonardo and April O'Neil in Nickelodeon All-Star Brawl, the fighting game due out this Fall for PlayStation platforms, Xbox platforms, Nintendo Switch, and PC.

#IGN #Gaming
